cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper proposes an online visual tracking algorithm using Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) and focuses on computer vision and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves learning and using SVM, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves constructing target-specific saliency maps, which can be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with image processing and segmentation, which can be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves backpropagation of features, which can be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
